    "name": "The Tunnels of Saint Mercy Road",
    "steam_appid": 3003530,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the classics of horror gaming, The Tunnels of Saint Mercy Road is a blend of psychological horror, atmospheric horror and creature horror that is certain to give you chills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003530/extras/b3fdaac6d780581731c44ade1d8af5db.avif?t=1729648045\" width=600 height=262 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The tunnels under Saint Mercy road are known for many things. Paranormal encounters... Mysterious cults... Monsters galore... The legends around town spread like a game of telephone. They can't all be true... can they?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>What if I told you that the truth can be revealed, but it would be a journey you have to take... <strong>ALONE</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Tunnels of Saint Mercy Road is an immersive horror experience that spans 8 unique areas, each providing a sense of unease and a new mystery to unravel.  Armed with only a lantern, you will descend into the tunnels under Saint Mercy road and explore it's depths and find clues to uncover the truth behind the local legends.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have the courage to descend into darkness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>I. Dare. You.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003530/extras/9b8fc062849297a685fab9bfe3535f20.avif?t=1729648045\" width=600 height=262 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An immersive, single player atmospheric experience (headphones suggested).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 unique areas that will give you a different sense of dread the further you delve. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles and complete objectives to descend further into the dark tunnels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stylized graphics - Re-experience classic horror with a modern first person take.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short Story - Can be completed in under two hours. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by classic horror games and literature.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepad Support - Play with your gamepad, keyboard and mouse or accessibility device.</p></li></ul>",
